Phthalates downloaded on June 19, 2008 at www.phthalates.org. 

6 J.  H.  Kin  et  al.,  ‘‘DEHP  migration  behavior  from  excessively  plasticized  PVC  sheets,’’  Bul-

letin of the Korean Chemical Society, 2003 Volume 24(3) 345–349. 

