Silent  Spring  Institute  and  Harvard  School  of  Public  Health,  ‘‘Phthalates,  Alkylphenols,  Pes-
ticides, Polybrominated Diphenyl Ethers and Other Endocrine Disrupting Compounds in Indoor 
Air and Dust,’’ Environmental Science and Technology 37:4543–4553, 15 October 2003 

