phthalate  esters  inhibits  fetal  testicular  testosterone  production  in  the  Sprague  Dawley  rat  in 
a  cumulative,  dose  additive  manner.’’  Toxicological  Sciences.  Accessed  June  19,  2008  at  http:// 
toxsci.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/kfn077. 

