file with the author. Our petition was later denied. 

29 Eight  of  the  toys  were  labeled  ‘‘phthalate-free’’  on  the  packaging.  One  item  was  labeled 
‘‘phthalate-free’’  on  the  manufacturer’s  website.  For  the  last  item,  the  manufacturer’s  website 
claimed not to use phthalates in any of its children’s products. 

